quran[83]{c,v,t}:
  36,1,"Yɑɑ Sɩɩn"
  36,2,"M wẽen ne Alkʋrãanã sẽn bʋ n manegã."
  36,3,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka fo bee tẽn-tʋʋmbã pʋgẽ."
  36,4,"N be so-tɩrg zugu."
  36,5,"N ya wilb Naabã sikri, sẽn yaa yolsg Naabã."
  36,6,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ f bugs neb b sẽn pa bugs b baab-rãmba, tɩ bãmb yaa yam yaal-yaal rãmba."
  36,7,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka gomdã sɩdga b wʋsg fãa zugu, tɩ bãmb pa kõt sɩd ye."
  36,8,"Ad Tõnd ninga b yubliẽ wã goala tɩ b tʋg n teeg b lεmã, tɩ b nensã nake."
  36,9,"La D ning koak b taoorã, la b poorẽ wã me koaka, n lud-b tɩ b pa neẽ ye."
  36,10,"La yaa a ye b zugu, fo bugs-b lame ma fo pa bugs-ba: b pa kõt sɩd ye."
  36,11,"Ad fo sẽn bugsdã yaa ned ning sẽn tũud-a tẽegrã, la a yaeesd Arrahmaan (yolsg) Naabã ne a sẽn lillã fãɑ. Bɩ f noog a sũur ne yaafa la keoor sẽn yaa bedre."
  36,12,"Ad Tõnd n vʋʋgd kũ-rãmbã, la D gʋlsd bũmb ning b sẽn tʋm tɩ reng taoorã, la b vũunã, la bũmbã fãa Tõnd tigim-a-la gaf vẽeneg pʋgẽ."
  36,13,"La f rɩk bilgr ne-ba, ne tẽngã rãmba, wakat ning tẽn-tʋʋmbã sẽn wa n wa-a wã."
  36,14,"Wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wa n tʋms neb a yiib b nengẽ, tɩ b yags b yiibã, tɩ Tõnd paas tãaben-soaba, tɩ b yeele: ""Ad tõnd yaa b sẽn tʋms-b rãmb yãmb nengẽ""."
  36,15,"Tɩ b yeele: ""yãmb pa yɩ rẽnda ninsaalb bal wala tõndo, la Arrahmaan Naab pa sik bɑɑ fʋɩ, yãmb pa yɩ rẽnda yagdb bala""."
  36,16,"Tɩ b yeele: ""tõnd Soabã miime tɩ ad tõnd yaa b sẽn tʋms-b rãmb yãmb nengẽ"","
  36,17,"La pa be tõnd zug rẽnda taas vẽeneg bala""."
  36,18,"Tɩ b yeele: ""wɩɩbd n paam tõnd yãmb yĩnga, la tɩ yãmb sã n pa base, d na lob-y neer-neere, la naong sẽn zabd na paam yãmba sẽn yi tõnd nengẽ""."
  36,19,"Tɩ b yeel: ""yãmb wɩɩbdã bee ne-yã. B tẽeg yãmb yĩng (la y yet woto?). Pa woto ye! Yãmb yaa neb sẽn yaa maan-n-zʋʋg rãmba""."
  36,20,"Tɩ rao yi tẽngã yaang n wa ne yãgbo, n yeele: ""mam neba! Tũ-y tẽn-tʋʋmbã'',"
  36,21,"Tũ-y neb nins sẽn pa kot-b yãmb keoorã, tɩ bãmb yaool n yaa kãndgdba."
  36,22,"La yaa bõe n tar maam tɩ m pa na n tũ Soab ning sẽn naan-a maamã, la yaool n yaa Yẽnda nengẽ la b na n lebs yãmbã?"
  36,23,"Rẽ yĩnga m na gãd soben-zẽms sẽn pa Yẽnda, tɩ Arrahmaan Naab sã n tʋll maam ne wẽnga, b sugsgã pa nafd maam bɑɑ fʋɩ! B pa fãagd maam me."
  36,24,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, wakat-kãngã m bee meneng sẽn vẽneg pʋgẽ."
  36,25,"Ad mam kõo sɩd ne yãmb Soabã, bɩ y kelg-ma""."
  36,26,"Tɩ b yeel-ɑ -b sẽn kʋ-ɑ poorẽ-; ""kẽ Arzãnã"". T'a yeele: "" kato! Mam nebã sã n ra bãngẽ pɑ são,"
  36,27,"Bũmb ning mam Soabã sẽn yaaf maamã la A naag maam b sẽn waoog-b rãmbã pʋgẽ"""
  36,28,"La Tõnd pa sik a nebã zug tãp-biis (soddaas) sẽn yi saasẽ b sẽn kʋ-ɑ wã poor ye. Tõnd pa yɩ n yaa sikdb me."
  36,29,"Pa yɩ rẽnda Kaas-vuk bal tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn ki."
  36,30,"Ad bõn be yembsã zugu, tẽn-tʋʋm buud pa wat b nengẽ rẽndame tɩ b yɩ n yaand-a."
  36,31,"Rẽ yĩnga, bãmb pa bãng tɩ sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn halk zãma-rãmb sẽn reng bãmb taoore, tɩ b pa le tõe n legb n wa bãmb nengẽ."
  36,32,"La b yenkãm fãa gilli, rẽndame tɩ b na n waa ne-a Tõnd nengẽ."
  36,33,"La tagmas sẽn na wilg bãmba, yaa tẽng koεεngã, Tõnd vʋʋgd-a lame la D yiisd a pʋgẽ bõn-bεεla, tɩ beenẽ la b rɩta."
  36,34,"La Tõnd maan a pʋgẽ tamarʋ-tɩɩse pʋt la siba, la D pus ko-ninã tẽngɑ pʋgẽ."
  36,35,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ b na rɩ a biisã, la bãmb nusã sẽn tʋm bũmb ninga. Rẽ yĩnga b pa na n pʋʋs barka?"
  36,36,"Yɩlgemd be ne Naab ning sẽn naan kõbgã gillã, sẽn yaa tẽngã sẽn bulsdi la sẽn yi bãmb mensẽ wã la bũmb ning b sẽn pa mi."
  36,37,"La tagmas sẽn na n wilg bãmba, yaa yʋngã. Tõnd yiisda windgã a pʋgẽ tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn be likẽ."
  36,38,"La wĩndgã zoetame n tʋg a tablg zĩigẽ, ad rẽnda yaa wilb Naabã kordgo, minim Naabã kordgo."
  36,39,"La Kiuugã Tõnd kord-a-la ne sigb zĩisi, hal t'a wa tʋg n lebg wala tamar gĩnɑ wilã sẽn kʋdge."
  36,40,"Pa segd ne Wĩndgã t'a paam Kiuugã, yʋngã me pa rengd wĩndgã; la b fãa be wεεng-vʋɩɩgẽ n rugda."
  36,41,"La tagmas sẽn na n wilg bãmba, Tõnd rɩka bãmb baab-rãmbã kogl-pitgã pʋgẽ."
  36,42,"La D naan sẽn wõnd rẽ n kõ-ba, b sẽn na zombe."
  36,43,"La d sã n da tʋllẽ, D bõrd-b lame, tɩ sõngd ka ne-b ye, tɩ b ka na n fãag-b me ye."
  36,44,"Sã n pa yolsg sẽn yi Tõnd nengẽ yĩnga la wʋm-noog n tʋg n tãag wakato."
  36,45,"La b sã n yeel-ba ""gũus-y bũmb ning sẽn be yãmb taoorã la sẽn be yãmb poorẽ wã tɩ sãnd-sãnde b na yols-yã""."
  36,46,"Lɑ Aɑyɑr buud pɑ be sẽn nɑ wɑ b nengẽ, sẽn yaa b Soɑbã Aɑyɑy rẽndɑme tɩ b yɩ bɑlldb n yi-ɑ."
  36,47,"La b sã n yeel-ba: ""yãk-y bũmb ning Wẽnd sẽn kõ yãmbã n nafe"". Sẽn kɩfl-bã yeta sẽn kõ-b sɩdã ""tõnd na rɩlg ned ning Wẽnd sẽn da na n rɩlg a soab t'A sã n da ratẽ? Yãmb pa be rẽnda meneng sẽn vẽneg pʋgẽ""."
  36,48,"La b yetẽ: ""yaa rabʋr la pʋleng-kãngã, tɩ y sã n togsda sɩda?"""
  36,49,"B pa kolld rẽnda Kaas-vuk bal tɩ rɩk-ba, n mik tɩ bãmb ra zabda taaba."
  36,50,"Tɩ b pa tõe n kõ sagelle, b pa lebg me n tʋg b nebẽ wã."
  36,51,"Tɩ b fʋʋs Bargẽ wã, tɩ bãmb yaa sẽn yit b yaadẽ wã n yãgd n tʋgd b Soabã nengẽ."
  36,52,"Tɩ b yeele: ""yaa tõnd wɩɩbdo! Ãnd n yik tõnd d gãasẽ wã?"" Yaa wãndã la Arrahmaan Naab sẽn pʋlmã, la tẽn-tʋʋmbã togsa sɩda."
  36,53,"Pa yɩ rẽnda Kaas-vuk bala, tɩ bãmb fãa gill yaa b sẽn na n wa ne Tõnd nengẽ."
  36,54,"La rũndã, b pa wẽgd yõor ba fʋɩ, la b pa rond-y me, rẽnda bũmb ning y sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  36,55,"Ad Arzãn koambã, rũndã b bee wʋm-noog soagl pʋga,"
  36,56,"Bãmb ne b pagb bee maasem pʋsẽ, n be gãas zut n kɩla."
  36,57,"B tara tɩ-biis a pʋgẽ, la b leb n tar b sẽn rat fãa."
  36,58,"""Salaam"" tɩlgr koεεg sẽn yi Soab nengẽ sẽn yaa Yolsda be ne bãmbɑ."
  36,59,"La lak-y rũnda, yaa yãmb a nin-wẽnse!"
  36,60,"Rẽ yĩnga M ra pa sagl yãmba, yaa yãmb Adam koamba, tɩ y ra tũ a Sʋɩtãanã? Tɩ ɑd a yaa bε sẽn vẽneg ne yãmba."
  36,61,"La y tũ Maam, wãnde la sor sẽn yɑɑ tɩrga."
  36,62,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka a menemsa yãmb pʋgẽ bõn-naands wʋsgo, rẽ yĩnga yãmb pa yɩ n paam yam?"
  36,63,"Wãnde la Gεhannem ning b sẽn da yɩ n pʋlem yãmbã."
  36,64,"Kẽ-y-yã-a rũnda, yãmb sẽn da yɩ n kɩfendẽ wã yĩnga."
  36,65,"Rũnda D sẽta b noyã tɩ b nusã gom ne Tõndo, tɩ b nãoã seet bũmb ning b sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  36,66,"La tɩ Tõnd sã n da tʋllẽ, D naaan n yẽes b ninã, tɩ b reng taab sorẽ wã, la b na n yãa wãn-wãna?."
  36,67,"La tɩ D sã n da tʋllẽ, D na n toeem b naanegã b zĩisẽ wã, tɩ b pa tõe n kẽnge, b pa tõe n lebg me."
  36,68,"La Tõnd sẽn wogl-a soab yõore, D boogd-a-la naanegã wɛɛngẽ, b pa tar yam la?."
  36,69,"La Tõnd pa wilg-a yɩɩl ye, la a pa sõmb ne-a me ye, a pa yɩ rẽnda tẽegr la Alkʋrãan sẽn vẽnege."
  36,70,"Bʋɩl yĩng t'a na bugs ned ning sẽn ya-a vɩta, la gomdã sɩdg kɩfr-rãmbã zugu."
  36,71,"Rẽ yĩnga bãmb pa yã tɩ Tõnd naana neema rũms n kõ-ba, sẽn yaa Tõnd Nus sẽn tʋme, tɩ bãmb n so-ba?"
  36,72,"La D nom-b n kõ-ba. Be b pʋgẽ b sẽn zombde, be b pʋgẽ me b sẽn rɩte."
  36,73,"La b leb n tar nafa b pʋgẽ la bõn-yũudi, b pa na n pʋʋs baaka?"
  36,74,"La b gãda soaben-dãmb zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, sãnd-sãnde b na sõng bãmba."
  36,75,"B pa tõe n sõng-b ye; pa rẽ meng ye, bãmb meng yɑɑ tãp-biis (sodaase) n gũud-ba, lɑ bãmb ne b rʋbsã yɑɑ wɑtbɑ bugmeẽ wã."
  36,76,"Bɩ b gomdã ra wa sãam fo sũur ye, ad Tõnd mii bũmb ning b sẽn solgdã la b sẽn vẽnegdã."
  36,77,"Rẽ yĩnga ninsaal pa yã tɩ Tõnd naan-a lame ne mani, la a sẽn yik n lebg tak-n-taar sẽn vẽneg soaba."
  36,78,"La a rɩk bilgr ne Tõndo, n yaool n yĩm a naanegã; n yeele: "" Ãnd n tõe n vʋʋg kõab tɩ b sã n kẽ bugdu?""."
  36,79,"Yeele: ""Soab ning sẽn yẽbg-a raẽenemã n vʋʋgd-a, la Yẽnd n yaa mit ne naaneg fãa""."
  36,80,"""Soab ning sẽn maan-a bugum n kõ yãmbã n yi tɩ-maasrẽ wã, tɩ yãmb yaa sẽn vidgd ne-a""."
  36,81,"Rẽ yĩnga Soab ning sẽn naan-a Saasã pa tõe n naan b bilgr sɩda? A toeeme! La Yẽnda la naaneg tõog Soaba n ya Mita."
  36,82,"Ad A sã n rat bũmbu, yaa A yeel-a bala: ""yɩ"" . T'a be yɩɩbẽ."
  36,83,"Rẽnd yɩlgemd be ne Naab ning bũmb fãa soolem sẽn be A Nugẽ wã, la Yẽ nengẽ la b na n lebs-yã."
